{"tid":1818523,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年十大最賺F2P遊戲 Fortnite勁賺18億美元","createTime":"2020-01-10T03:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T23:35:22.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"94001ff082edd3cd4842e77de0209764e6055cd3","tid":1818523,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2535000/2537691/20200109_wes_topten07_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2535000%2F2537691%2F20200109_wes_topten07_1024.jpg&h=00fc2de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年最賺錢的十大免費遊戲是哪幾隻？相信不少人都心中有數，但賺錢到甚麼程度，大家可以看看市場調查公司SuperData的最新數據。<br />\n<br />\n2019年十大最賺F2P遊戲<br />\nFortnite首位<br />\n王者榮耀第三<br />\n最近幾年手機遊戲及Free 2 Play遊戲發展蓬勃，要求玩家課金隨機開箱、購買季票的作品愈來愈多，亦有部分廠商愈來愈無恥，令歐美國家開始研究立法手段進行監管。市場調查公司SuperData最近發表了2019年十大最賺F2P遊戲，當中首位不出意外是人氣急升的Fortnite，營收１８億美元，第２位是韓國原產的Dungeon and Fighter（Arad戰記）收入１６億美元、第３位是收入１６億美元的王者榮耀，接下來才是英雄聯盟１５億美元。<br />\n<br />\n至於第５位至１０位如下：<br />\n5.Candy Crush Saga - 15億<br />\n6.Pokemon Go - 14億<br />\n7.Crossfire - 14億<br />\n8.Fate/Grand Order - 12億<br />\n9.Game for Peace 12億<br />\n10.Last Shelter:Survival 11億<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2535000/2537691/20200109_wes_topten03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2535000%2F2537691%2F20200109_wes_topten03_600.jpg&h=d3d71e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一方面，報告又提到手遊、ＰＣ、主機３方的收入，分別為644億、296億及154億。比例上每5美元就有4元是Free 2 Play遊戲產生，整個市場收入年均增長約４％。報告又提到將ＡＡＡ級大作帶到流動平台上是成功的策略，點名提及Call of Duty及Mario Kart:World Tour。而2月發表的Apex Legends亦有被提及它的突破性宣傳手法，成功爭取玩家焦點及首月9100萬的收入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2535000/2537691/20200109_wes_topten02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2535000%2F2537691%2F20200109_wes_topten02_600.jpg&h=48725238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2535000/2537691/20200109_wes_topten04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2535000%2F2537691%2F20200109_wes_topten04_600.jpg&h=a74ff7d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d28e4953a67b1af6c4ccecde13d157beb589d5cb","tid":1818523,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9176d7f5286ab901385871fdab4141da41196ec","tid":1818523,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9f18b6a9eca328431df39dda152a43708b059bf","tid":1818523,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5L9O9XT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5L9O9XT.jpg&h=1dcce04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你畸形到 pc加console都唔夠手機多錢"},{"pid":"3d1cb7e48bbcffe0983b4864d59efebea81186dc","tid":1818523,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kx0VPYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKx0VPYr.jpg&h=b67a11c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b26878842bccf028bdb558b339a29810859c392","tid":1818523,"uid":293376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"全部都係垃圾GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53118729fb652c72133c35965fa5ea272a460af","tid":1818523,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"劣幣<br />\nso9sad"},{"pid":"6287669f6b8df70f560789ceb5edaa168